Document the vcc-supply and iovcc-supply properties of the Rocktech
jh057n00900 panel.

Signed-off-by: Guido GÃ¼nther <agx@sigxcpu.org>
Reviewed-by: Sam Ravnborg <sam@ravnborg.org>
Signed-off-by: Sam Ravnborg <sam@ravnborg.org>
